@page
@model ProductsModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Products";
}

<div>
    <h2>Eco-Friendly Products</h2>
    <p>Explore our range of eco-friendly products, each carefully selected to promote sustainability without compromising on quality. At ABC Retail, we are committed to offering items that are not only good for you but also good for the planet.</p>

    <div class="product">
        <h3>Product 1: Eco-Friendly Cup</h3>
        <img src="~/images/eco-friendly-cup.jpg" alt="Eco-Friendly Cup" class="img-fluid" style="width: 700px; height: auto;" />
        <p>Our Eco-Friendly Cup is crafted from sustainable materials, providing an environmentally responsible alternative to traditional cups. It's perfect for those who want to make a positive impact while enjoying their favorite beverages.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="product">
        <h3>Product 2: Advanced Gadget</h3>
        <img src="~/images/advance-gadgets.jpg" alt="Advanced Gadget" class="img-fluid" style="width: 700px; height: auto;" />
        <p>Discover the Advanced Gadget, designed to enhance your lifestyle with cutting-edge technology. With its user-friendly interface and reliable performance, it’s the perfect addition to any tech enthusiast's collection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="product">
        <h3>Product 3: Eco-Friendly Accessory</h3>
        <img src="~/images/eco-accessory.jpg" alt="Eco-Friendly Accessory" class="img-fluid" style="width: 700px; height: auto;" />
        <p>Our Eco-Friendly Accessory combines sustainability with style. Made from recycled materials, it’s the ideal choice for environmentally conscious consumers who don't want to compromise on quality.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="product">
        <h3>Product 4: Innovative Tool</h3>
        <img src="~/images/eco-tool.jpg" alt="Innovative Tool" class="img-fluid" style="width: 700px; height: auto;" />
        <p>The Innovative Tool is engineered for precision and efficiency. Perfect for professionals and hobbyists alike, this tool offers superior performance and reliability for all your needs.</p>
    </div>
</div>
